snippet.title: Ultimate Bomb Squad - Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Ultimate Bomb Squad is a fast-paced loud stealth platformer where you have to be fast  and be careful, because every sound you make has consequences. 

Defuse bombs, deceive enemies, avoid hazards, shoot and shout your way to save the day now, tomorrow and yesterday.

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1445850/Ultimate_Bomb_Squad/
